title: The Harbinger - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 10/8/21
itunes:title: The Harbinger - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 10/8/21
description:
Guest host Richard Syrett and author Jonathan Cahn discuss his book "The Harbinger," which examines the biblical prophesies that seem to predict the terrorist attacks of September 11, and how the symbolism of the Pentagon and World Trade Center are connected to continuing unrest in America today.
